n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=fbee57c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"3d2d4c09c1f7ee828a7aee78d035a1c83c20582b","tid":1278660,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾會塊玻璃要半億？開條數黎睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e946c333083dcf182049c3c3f52ab0879acb838","tid":1278660,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2042b667491bc0d74e00deb9223de3df4fde3480","tid":1278660,"uid":12244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e946c333083dcf182049c3c3f52ab0879acb838","tid":1278660,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"1.5億<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"ac4e183257959f305b4b7f71b0f65b0c433487c6","tid":1278660,"uid":26307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"